                <div class="homepage-left-content">
                    <div class="numbered-title step-one-icon">We do the work for you</div>
                    <div class="steps-text">If you're just using job boards for your job search, you could be missing out on the 70% of "hidden" job openings which are never publicly advertised. <span class="expanded-help-text" style="display:none;">Uploading your resume to LinkMe allows employers and recruiters to match you to jobs you didn't even know were out there. </span><span class="expand-link more-link js_expand-help" onclick="javascript:expandHelp(this);">more</span></div>
